WEBVTT

00:05:59.043 --> 00:06:03.806
She would be getting late
for work, she was always busy

00:06:03.806 --> 00:06:06.244
we would be going to school,
college, she would be cooking.

00:06:06.244 --> 00:06:08.539
So my image of my mother is of her

00:06:08.563 --> 00:06:13.274
in a blouse and petticoat draping
a saree while working

00:06:13.460 --> 00:06:17.122
It is because of her that I can
drape a saree very well.

00:06:17.122 --> 00:06:17.502
AK: Really!

00:06:17.502 --> 00:06:21.077
SRK: Genuinely, I can drape a saree very well.

00:06:21.077 --> 00:06:22.996
And this offer is open to all the ladies!

00:06:23.027 --> 00:06:27.087
(Laughter and applause)

00:06:27.727 --> 00:06:31.314
AK: Genuinely, I feel that 
we always talk about Durga.